<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="实战案例！腾讯文档在线收集表设计复盘总结" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-388630" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/uisdc-tx-20200913-93.jpg" alt="实战案例！腾讯文档全平台系统设计复盘" width="180" height="184" /></span></p>
